maludb (0.40.0-1) noble; urgency=medium

  * v1.6.0 release surface. Extension upgrade chain
    0.1.0 → 0.2.0 → … → 0.40.0 (40 migration steps).
  * Stages 2..6 in-DB feature set landed:
    - Stage 2 memory object model + derivation ledger.
    - Stage 3 bitemporal + supersession + SVPOR + MAUT + lifecycle.
    - Stage 4 retrieval planner + FTS/graph/hints + 3-stage authz.
    - Stage 5 workflow extraction + skill runtime + active pools +
      episode replay.
    - Stage 6 local-node sync + model registry blue-green +
      adapter alignment + advanced MC2DB tools.
  * Stage 7 hardening underway: benchmark baseline, security review,
    getting-started + admin docs + four end-to-end examples.
  * 50/50 pg_regress tests pass on PG 17.

